videos.description: Georgia Tech's running back KirVonte Benson powers through several defenders after contact.
videos.headline: Benson carry's defenders for a 16-yard run

videos.description: Georgia Tech's QB TaQuon Marshall punches in the 1-yard touchdown on the QB keeper.
videos.headline: Marshall runs it up the middle for TD

videos.description: Tennessee's Evan Berry returns kickoff 51 yards, putting the Volunteers in great field position.
videos.headline: Berry returns kick into Ga Tech territory

videos.description: Tennessee's Daniel Bituli strips Ta Quon Marshall and the Volunteers recover.
videos.headline: Marshall fumbles on keeper

videos.description: Tennessee ties the game at 7 on John Kelly's 1-yard run.
videos.headline: Kelly leaps in for TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech's KirVonte Benson plows through defender to give Yellow Jackets the lead.
videos.headline: Benson hammers through defender for TD

videos.description: Tennessee head coach Butch Jones elaborates on what his team needs to better in the second half.
videos.headline: Butch Jones breaks down what Tennessee needs to improve on

videos.description: The Yellow Jackets are in the lead after two touchdowns on the ground.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tennessee-Georgia Tech Halftime) 2017/9/5 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Georgia Tech leads No. 25 Tennessee at half

videos.description: Georgia Tech's TaQuon Marshall fakes the option, cuts up the field for a big gain.
videos.headline: Marshall weaves through defenders on long run

videos.description: Georgia Tech's TaQuon Marshall squeaks into the end zone on a quarterback keeper up the middle.
videos.headline: Marshall with another TD on the ground

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Nathan Cottrell shows off his speed on a 38-yard run.
videos.headline: Cottrell cuts up field for big gain on option

videos.description: Tennessee's John Kelly breaks free for a 30 yard run to the Georgia Tech 5-yard line.
videos.headline: Kelly puts Tennessee in scoring range on run

videos.description: Tennessee's Quinten Normady connects with Marquez Callaway for a touchdown to pull with 7.
videos.headline: Dormady's 10-yard TD strike narrows deficit

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Qua Searcy catches 42-yard pass down the seam to put Yellow Jackets in scoring position.
videos.headline: Marshall tosses deep ball to get back into red zone

videos.description: Georgia Tech's TaQuan Marshall dives for the pylon for his third rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Marshall bounces outside for another TD

videos.description: Tennessee's Marquez Callaway spins by a defender and cruises down the sideline to keep the Volunteers in the game.
videos.headline: Callaway speeds down sideline for 50-yard TD catch

videos.description: Georgia Tech's QB TaQuon Marshall comes up with a left arm injury after short run.
videos.headline: Marshall gets shaken up on short run

videos.description: Tennessee's Rasheen Gaulden strips J.J. Green of the ball and the Volunteers recover.
videos.headline: Gaulden causes fumble, Tennessee recovers

videos.description: Tennessee tops off 93-yard drive with a 10-yard touchdown run by John Kelly.
videos.headline: Kelly's 10-yard run ties game late for Vols

videos.description: Shawn Davis' game-winning field goal is blocked as time expires to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Tennessee blocks Ga Tech's game-winning field goal

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall's touchdown gets Georgia Tech ahead on the first overtime possession.
videos.headline: Marshall forces way in for 4th TD

videos.description: Tennessee's John Kelly extends the game after reaching the end zone on a short run.
videos.headline: Kelly forces 2OT with 1-yard TD

videos.description: Tennessee take the lead in double overtime on John Kelly' 2-yard run.
videos.headline: Kelly puts Vol's on top with 2nd TD in OT

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall jukes by a defender for a 13-yard touchdown in second overtime.
videos.headline: Marshall eludes defender for TD in 2OT

videos.description: Georgia Tech comes up short on game-winning 2-point conversion and falls to Tennessee 42-41.
videos.headline: Ga Tech's 2-point attempt for the win comes up short

videos.description: Butch Jones breaks down Tennessee's double-overtime victory over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Butch Jones talks about 'grit' in Vols win

videos.description: Scott Van Pelt and Kirk Herbstreit agree with Georgia Tech head coach Paul Johnson's decision to go for the win, despite it not working out.
